description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey.

Edited and produced in the UK by Rachel Shelley.


Here's to a Happier New Year, and a sneaky look back to where it all began...


Enormous thanks to our amazing listeners for supporting us on this wild PANTS ride.

We love you!

Stay safe, stay tuned.

Stay positive.
